uare so i had to be a little careful to avoid getting stuff bunched up. but i managed to make it work!</p>\n<p>i did get bored halfway through but i had enough time to convince myself that i would be better off finishing the project up and not having to think about it anymore</p>"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}